    <item>
      <title>随着美国审查力度加大，微软和苹果避开 OpenAI 董事会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/microsoft-quits-openai-board-after-antitrust-scrutiny-grows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[微软公司和苹果公司放弃了成为 OpenAI 董事会观察员的机会，这一令人惊讶的决定凸显了反垄断监管机构对大型科技公司对人工智能影响力的审查日益严格。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/microsoft-quits-openai-board-after-antitrust-scrutiny-grows</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 05:29:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>百度自动驾驶出租车订单激增，看涨期权飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/baidu-shares-surge-in-hong-kong-as-robotaxi-orders-increase</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于有迹象表明百度的 Apollo Go 自动驾驶出租车在中国越来越受欢迎，百度股价创下一年多以来的最大涨幅，看涨期权押注也飙升至历史新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/baidu-shares-surge-in-hong-kong-as-robotaxi-orders-increase</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 02:58:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲股市最大跌幅使泰国创始人失去亿万富翁地位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/asia-s-biggest-stock-drop-erases-thai-ev-tycoon-from-billionaire-status</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两年前，泰国最大的可再生能源生产商之一 Somphote Ahunai 的净资产曾突破 48 亿美元。但在经历了一系列艰难的努力后，该公司已不再是亿万富翁，因为该公司试图将自己定位为像特斯拉那样的运输专家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/asia-s-biggest-stock-drop-erases-thai-ev-tycoon-from-billionaire-status</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 02:00:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国际电气因 KKR 出售计划上市以来股价暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/kokusai-electric-plunges-by-most-since-listing-on-kkr-sale-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据报道，KKR&amp;Co. 计划出售其在日本芯片设备制造商国际电气株式会社 (Kokusai Electric Corp.) 的部分股份，受此消息影响，该公司股价一度下跌 12%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/kokusai-electric-plunges-by-most-since-listing-on-kkr-sale-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 01:51:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克在推特大规模裁员案中胜诉，赔偿 5 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/musk-beats-500-million-severance-suit-over-mass-twitter-layoff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[X Corp. 及其所有者埃隆·马斯克击败了亿万富翁于 2022 年 10 月收购社交媒体平台后解雇数千名员工而提起的其中一项诉讼。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/musk-beats-500-million-severance-suit-over-mass-twitter-layoff</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 01:10:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>三星工人计划“无限期”罢工，全球科技业面临风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/samsung-labor-union-says-prepared-to-strike-indefinitely</link>
      <description><![CDATA[三星电子公司最大的工会拥有超过 30,000 名工人，该工会宣布无限期罢工，这一意外举动加大了这家全球最大内存芯片制造商的生产中断风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/samsung-labor-union-says-prepared-to-strike-indefinitely</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 00:58:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>休斯顿努力应对贝丽尔的停电和酷热</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/lumen-s-houston-data-center-having-disruptions-amid-power-woes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[休斯顿正在努力应对飓风贝丽尔造成的混乱后果，预计风暴洪水退去后，停电、道路阻塞、互联网中断和天然气供应不稳定等状况仍将持续。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/lumen-s-houston-data-center-having-disruptions-amid-power-woes</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 18:36:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国人工智能热潮推动台湾科技出口激增 422%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/ai-boom-drives-fastest-growth-in-taiwanese-exports-since-2022</link>
      <description><![CDATA[人工智能的蓬勃发展正推动台湾出口激增，去年台湾企业出货了价值超过 420 亿美元的图形处理单元和相关设备，而近年来这一数字几乎为零。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/ai-boom-drives-fastest-growth-in-taiwanese-exports-since-2022</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 09:13:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>北京立法允许自动驾驶出租车，反对声不断</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/beijing-legislates-for-robotaxis-as-backlash-against-them-climbs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着高级驾驶辅助系统在中国变得越来越普及，北京将支持在城市网约车和汽车租赁车队中引入自动驾驶出租车。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/beijing-legislates-for-robotaxis-as-backlash-against-them-climbs</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 06:41:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
